txt.en: Many young fire-drakes are born within the caverns of Nargroth, gaining strength before they leave their nests. If the plateau of Gorgoroth is ever to become safe, you will need to defeat fire-drakelings and their nests.
Nargroth is located in Talath Úrui.\n\nYou should defeat fire-drakelings and destroy drakeling nests in Nargroth.
Defeated fire-drakelings and destroyed drakeling nests in Nargroth.
Nargroth is located in Talath Úrui.\n\nYou should defeat fire-drakelings and destroy drakeling nests in Nargroth.
Nargroth, the caverns of fire, is home to many creatures of flame.
You have successfully defeated many fire-drakelings and destroyed their nests in Nargroth. Your efforts should be felt in Mordor as the number of drakes dwindle.
